---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Senderismo puerto varas | Guias completas" description="Guias completas de senderismo en puerto varas. Informacion actualizada con tips locales.">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6D28D9 0%, #DB2777 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-20">
      <span class="text-5xl mb-4 block">🥾</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4">Senderismo</h1>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl">Todo lo que necesitas saber antes de ir.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6" set:html={`<a href="/senderismo/trekking-volcan-osorno" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Avanzada</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">Conquista el Gigante Andino</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Camina hasta el cráter del Volcán Osorno con vistas al Lago Llanquihue</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ 6-8 horas</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 45 km (1 hora)</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Diciembre a marzo</span></div></div></a>
      <a href="/senderismo/sendero-laguna-verde-puerto-varas" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Baja a moderada</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">Paseo al Espejo Esmeralda</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Caminata fácil a una laguna glaciar de aguas verdes</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ 3-4 horas ida y vuelta</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 70 km (1.5 horas)</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Octubre a abril</span></div></div></a>
      <a href="/senderismo/ruta-cerro-philippi-puerto-varas" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Avanzada a técnica</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">La Montaña Olvidada de Puerto Varas</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Ascenso técnico al Cerro Philippi con vistas privilegiadas</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ 8-10 horas</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 55 km (1.5 horas)</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Enero a marzo</span></div></div></a>
      <a href="/senderismo/sendero-bosque-enchante-puerto-varas" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Fácil</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">Camina Entre Héroes de Cuento</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Sendero único con esculturas de madera en medio del bosque</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ 1.5 horas</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 12 km (20 minutos)</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Todo el año</span></div></div></a>
      <a href="/senderismo/trekking-islabo-puerto-varas" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Moderada</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">Explora la Isla Misteriosa del Lago</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Aventura en kayak y caminata por una isla desierta del Lago Llanquihue</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ Día completo con tour</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 30 minutos en lancha</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Noviembre a abril</span></div></div></a>
      <a href="/senderismo/ruta-ensenada-puerto-varas" class="group block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden no-underline hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center relative"><span class="text-5xl">🥾</span><span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-white/90 text-xs font-medium px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Fácil (en auto) a moderada (en bicicleta)</span></div><div class="p-6"><h2 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors mb-2">Panorámicas que Quitan el Aliento</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Caminata por la ruta de los miradores hacia Ensenada</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">⏱️ 3-4 horas ida y vuelta</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">📍 45 km a Ensenada</span><span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">🗓️ Todo el año</span></div></div></a>`}></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>